title: Money With Michelle; Preparing For Tax Season!
description:
We all know that spring is the most dreaded time of the year... TAX SEASON! Michelle is joining us today to talk about how to prepare for tax season as a hairdresser and gives tips on things you should know to make this time of year a whole lot easier. Don't forget to follow him on instagram so you can message him with questions you have about your business!
